verse.word_meanings:
(एभिः) by the influence of Sattvik Sri Vishnu, the work of these (गुणमयैः) qualities, by the influence of Rajas Sri Brahma and by the power of Tamas Sri Shiva (त्रिभिः) with three kinds of emotions (इदम्) this (सर्वम्) all (जगत् ) The world - the community of creatures (maam) in the net of Me (mohitam) is being fascinated, i.e. (ebhyaḥ) therefore (param avyayam) full indestructible (n) does not (abhijanati) know.
The function forms of these qualities: By the influence of Sattvic Sri Vishnu, by the influence of Rajas Sri Brahma and Tamas by the influence of Tamas, this whole world - Pranisamudaaya is being fascinated in the net of time, i.e., trapped, therefore he does not know the complete indestructible.
 {Parameshwar Kabir Bandi Chhod Ji Ki Mahima Sant Garibdas Ji has said and explains the web of time:- Garib, Brahma Vishnu Mahesh, Maya and Dharmaraya (time). These five mills have made the voice of our voice.}
